             were indicted for <rs id="t17910112-41-off220" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910112-41-off220" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910112-41-off220" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17910112-41-cd221" type="crimeDate">17th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910112-41-off220 t17910112-41-cd221"></join>, six yards of black lace, value 15 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17910112-41-victim444" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Slack
                  <interp inst="t17910112-41-victim444" type="surname" value="Slack"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910112-41-victim444" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
